item.description:
 Create a Jira API key.
In AWS, create a new Secrets Manager secret called JiraApi in the same account/region as Squyre is deployed. Use the following content, obviously substituting your key and email. The secret should be of type Other type of secret.
{ &#34;apikey&#34;: &lt;the API key you just created&gt;, &#34;user&#34;: &lt;the email address of the Jira account the key is associated with&gt; }
